msgid "Scenario VI: Return to Where Doom Awaits"
msgstr "冒险VI：重返毁灭之地"

msgid "The lead investigator may choose an investigator to add the Naomi O'Bannion asset to their deck. This card does not count toward that investigator's deck size."
msgstr "队长可以选择一位调查员将娜奥米·欧巴尼恩支援卡加入其牌组。该卡牌不计入调查员的卡牌张数。"

msgid "Put Base of the Hill <i>(Warped and Twisted)</i>, Ascending Path <i>(Warped and Twisted)</i>, and Sentinel Peak into play. Remove the original Base of the Hill and Ascending Path locations from the game. Each investigator begins play at Base of the Hill."
msgstr "将山脚<i>(扭转曲折)</i>、上山道路<i>(扭转曲折)</i>和哨兵峰放置入场。将原版的山脚和上山道路地点移出游戏。每位调查员从山脚开始游戏。"

msgid "Remove 2 copies of Diverging Path from the game, at random. Set the other 3 copies of Diverging Path aside, out of play."
msgstr "随机选择2张分岔路移出游戏。将剩余3张放在一边，位于场外。"

msgid "Remove 2 copies of Altered Path from the game, at random. Set the other 3 copies of Altered Path aside, out of play."
msgstr "随机选择2张迷幻小路移出游戏。将剩余3张放在一边，位于场外。"

msgid "Set Seth Bishop and Naomi O'Bannion aside, out of play."
msgstr "将赛斯·毕晓普、娜奥米·欧巴尼恩放在一边，位于场外。"
